Package com.telenav.mesakit.graph.specifications.library.attributes

package com.telenav.mesakit.graph.specifications.library.attributes
  • Class
    Description
    Attribute<T>
    An attribute of an AttributeStore, having a name and an automatically assigned identifier.
    AttributeList
    Maintains a list of attributes in alphabetically sorted order to make reading them easier.
    AttributeLoader
    Loads attributes from a FieldArchive (note that GraphArchive is a field archive) and populates the fields of an AttributeStore through AttributeReference objects.
    AttributeReference<Referent extends com.telenav.kivakit.interfaces.naming.NamedObject & com.telenav.kivakit.interfaces.lifecycle.Initializable>
    Manages a referent (a value that's referred to by a reference) Attributes in an AttributeStore.
    AttributeSet
     
    AttributeStore
    A store of attributes which is loaded with an AttributeLoader.
